description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare French Phantoms & Crazy Creatures Edition

Dave & Tim are joined by our foreign correspondent to report on French Phantoms, and did we mention the weirdest creatures we have recently heard of? Acid Spraying Land Lobsters from Hell, Cannibal Ants, and a Jelly-fish like creature that makes a real a**hole of themselves, UFO Motherships over Vegas, NASA Astronauts & Uri Geller witness UFOs and Alien corpses!
All that PLUS your stories and a Brand New Theater of the Mind!

Come see Dave next at Michigan ParaCon: www.MIParacon.com
